Variety-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-XCX-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-XCX-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-XCX-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Charli-XCX-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_Variety-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>今天（9 月 2 日）在社交媒体上发布新帖子，正式宣布“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat”</a>夏季结束。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">这是 Charli XCX 的世界，我们只是生活在其中：到目前为止“Brat”夏天的时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p>Charli XCX 的第七张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">《Brat》</a>自六月发行以来一直处于<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">其自身文化现象</a>的中心。其简单的柠檬绿艺术作品成为了一种文化基因，而社交媒体上的粉丝也接受了这张唱片的享乐主义美学和态度。</p><p>在乔·拜登支持卡马拉·哈里斯作为 2024 年美国总统竞选的继任者后，<a href="https://x.com/charli_xcx/status/1815182384066707861">查利·XCX 在推特上发了一条</a>“卡马拉是小子”的推文，导致政治专家尴尬地<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-cnn-attempt-to-explain-the-kamala-is-brat-charli-xcx-memes-3777048">试图解释“小子”现象，但未能解释</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">她的专辑在这个夏天引起了无数关注，</a>其中之一就是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">查佩尔·罗恩 (Chappell Roan)</a>分享了一张拿着《Brat》CD 的自拍照，让歌迷们相信她将出现在即将推出的 Charli 歌曲中，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-charli-xcx-bring-brat-summer-to-ibiza-for-party-girl-boiler-room-set-3779693">Charli 最近将这张专辑带到了伊维萨岛锅炉房的“派对女孩”风格布景</a>。</p><p> 《小子》还获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mercury-prize-2024-check-out-the-shortlisted-nominees-here-3777869">水星奖提名</a>，并获得了广泛的好评，获得了一系列五星级和四星级的评论。</p><p>现在，查理在社交媒体上宣布“小子”夏天正式结束，并写道：“永远再见小子夏天。”</p><p>这位音乐家还在 Instagram 上分享了一系列片段，展示了《Brat》夏季的一些关键时刻，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tiktok">在 TikTok 上</a>随着《Apple》而火爆的舞蹈。在这里查看它们：</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">永远再见小子夏天。</p><p> — Charli (@charli_xcx) <a href="https://twitter.com/charli_xcx/status/1830695037925237025?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 9 月 2 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C_bVaeQPo7B/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="eveno